title: The Journal of Sir Walter Scott; From the Original Manuscript at Abbotsford
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: _January_ 23.--I wrought a little to-day. Walked to Chiefswood, orrather from it, as far only as Habbie's Howe. Came home, cold indeed,but hearty.
